Get down there. Now. go!

513
00:53:35.148 --> 00:53:38.818
Oh. come on!
Come on come on come on.

514
00:53:39.986 --> 00:53:45.116
OK. alright.
OK. we're gonna have to make a break for it.

515
00:53:45.200 --> 00:53:48.328
OK? Everybody ready?

516
